ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">You're in a stronger position than most early-career candidates then. Let me map out what you actually have:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Portfolio (complete picture):</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Off-ball movement &amp; attacking threat (flagship — tracking data)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Regain → Progression Pipeline (transitions)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Role Clustering + interactive Streamlit app (technical + ML)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Portland Thorns opposition analysis (applied football intelligence)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Master's project (academic credibility)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Transition Trigger / RDI — Argentina 2022 (in planning)</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Experience:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">US Mondorf (video scouting)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Portland Thorns (opposition analysis)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Athenians FC (player)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">NHS (pattern recognition, stakeholder communication)</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Honest assessment:</strong>
You don't have a portfolio problem. You have a visibility and packaging 
problem. The work is there — the question is whether it's being 
presented in a way that makes the full picture obvious in 60 seconds.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">One
 thing worth asking — how is your Master's project positioned? Because 
depending on the topic, that could actually be your strongest 
credibility piece and might be underused.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">What was it on?</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
