          ease-[cubic-bezier(0.165,0.85,0.45,1)] h-8 w-8 rounded-md group/btn _fill_10ocf_9 _ghost_10ocf_96" type="button" data-testid="action-bar-copy" aria-label="Copy"><div class="relative text-text-500 group-hover/btn:text-text-100"><div class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="flex-shrink: 0;" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12.5 3A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 14 4.5V6h1.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 17 7.5v8a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 6 15.5V14H4.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 12.5v-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 3zm1.5 9.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H7v1.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5H14zM4.5 4a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5z"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute top-0 left-0 transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="flex-shrink: 0;" class="absolute top-0 left-0 transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15.188 5.11a.5.5 0 0 1 .752.626l-.056.084-7.5 9a.5.5 0 0 1-.738.033l-3.5-3.5-.064-.078a.501.501 0 0 1 .693-.693l.078.064 3.113 3.113 7.15-8.58z"></path></svg></div></div></button></div><div class="flex items-center"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-test-render-count="2"><div class="group" style="height: auto; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="contents"><div data-is-streaming="false" class="group relative relative pb-3" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">This is genuinely impressive for an MSc project. A few things stand out:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>What's strong:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Live deployed Streamlit app is a big deal — most candidates have notebooks, you have a working product</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">The limitations section shows intellectual honesty that senior analysts respect</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Tchouaméni misclassification example is smart to include — it shows you understand <em>why</em> the model behaves as it does, not just how to run it</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Multi-league coverage across La Liga, Ligue 1, Serie A shows scale</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>The underused asset here:</strong>
This is your Master's thesis and it's sitting quietly in a GitHub 
README. It should be a LinkedIn post on its own. A carousel breaking 
down:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">The problem you were solving</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">One surprising finding</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">What the app actually does</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Link to the live dashboard</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">That's highly shareable content in the sports analytics space.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>One practical question:</strong>
Is the Streamlit app still live and working? Because a broken link on a 
portfolio is worse than no link. Worth checking before any recruiter 
visits it.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Honest overall view:</strong>
You have Ioannis — you have a Master's thesis, a live app, tracking data
 analysis, opposition analysis experience at a professional club, and a 
SkillCorner shortlisting. The portfolio isn't the problem anymore.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">The job now is making sure everything is packaged so someone can understand your full value in 60 seconds.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Have you got a personal website pulling it all together?</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
