<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">On the LinkedIn URL — your public profile link will look like <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">linkedin.com/in/ioannis-kastritis</code>
