ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">On desktop:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click your profile picture → <strong>View profile</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Look at the browser address bar</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">It'll show something like <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">linkedin.com/in/ioannis-kastritis-xxxx</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Copy that whole URL and paste it here</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">On mobile:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to your profile</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Tap the <strong>three dots</strong> (···) near the top</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Tap <strong>Contact info</strong> or <strong>Share profile</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">The URL will be visible there</li>
</ol>
