ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div class="pl-2 pt-1 pb-2"><div class="font-ui bg-bg-000 rounded-2xl rounded-t-3xl overflow-hidden border-border-300 border -mx-1 mb-4 transition-colors focus-within:border-accent-200/50 focus-within:shadow-md"><div class="flex flex-col"><div class="overflow-y-auto max-h-[400px]"><div style="opacity: 1; filter: blur(0px); transform: none;"><textarea placeholder="Write your message..." class="px-5 pt-4 pb-4 w-full resize-none bg-transparent border-none text-sm text-text-100 placeholder:text-text-500 !outline-none !ring-0" style="min-height: 200px;">Geia
 sou, efxaristo poli gia to feedback — xairomai pou to vikes endiaferon!

Exeis apoli dikio kai sta dio. To xThreat horizon einai pragma pou me 
apasxolise ki emena — an ena run arxizei apo vathi thesi, iparxei 
kindinios na min prolavaini na axiologithei swsta mesa sto parathiro ton
 10 defterolefton. Tha ithela na diaforopoiiso ta runs me vasi tin 
arxiki thesi gia na do an afto epireazei ta apotelesmata.

Oso gia to context isolation, einai kati pou me provlimatize — to 
support run se finishing phase exei telios diaforetiki logiki apo ena 
support run se build-up. Nomizo oti o diaxorismos kata phase of play tha
 edine poli pio akrivei axiologiseis.

Mia erotisi apo mena: sto diko sou mintialo me ta tracking dedomena, pos
 proserxeste to thema tou context — xrisimopoieite kapio tagging kata 
phase i to antimetopizetai me allon tropo?</textarea></div></div><div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 px-2 py-2"><div class="flex items-center h-8 bg-bg-000 rounded-lg border-0.5 border-border-300 shadow-sm overflow-hidden"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
