ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Yes, exactly that order.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Why Argentina (Transition Trigger) first:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">It's the most original piece — custom metric, your own concept</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">It directly addresses his feedback about context and phase of play</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">It will impress a SkillCorner person specifically because it uses tracking-derived thinking</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">It's a standalone project — cleaner to build and publish quickly</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Then Portland Thorns case study:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">More time-consuming to do properly</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Needs clean visuals and a coach-facing PDF</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Better as the second project so you have time to do it right</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Then contact him.</strong> By that point you'll have:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Live portfolio website</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Off-ball movement project (already done)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Transition Trigger / RDI — Argentina (new)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Portland Thorns case study (new)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Clustering app (already live)</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">That's a completely different candidate to the one he interviewed. And your message to him will be natural and easy:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><em>"Πήρα
 το feedback σου και δούλεψα πάνω σε δύο νέα projects — ένα για 
defensive transitions με custom metric και ένα applied opposition 
analysis. Θα χαρώ να ακούσω τη γνώμη σου."</em></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Short, confident, no begging. Just evidence.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>How long realistically do you think the Argentina project will take you?</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
