</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>This changes the project significantly for the better.</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">What
 you're not doing is building something from scratch to impress 
recruiters. You're taking a tool you already built for real analytical 
work and applying it to a public dataset so you can show it publicly. 
That's exactly what professional analysts do.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>The narrative writes itself:</strong></p>
