 developed this metric originally as part of an applied opposition 
analysis workflow. Here I apply it to Argentina's 2022 World Cup 
campaign using StatsBomb open data."</em></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">That one sentence tells Mike:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">You built tools for real purposes, not just portfolios</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">You can transfer methodology across contexts</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Your work has practical roots</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Practically what you need to do:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
