<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Regain → Progression card wrong shape</strong> — it's currently set to <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">grid-column: 1 / -1; max-width: 50%</code> which makes it odd. I'll fix it to match the others</li>
