<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">The official warning that his mother doesn't know about the tattoo yet</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">"Legally binding in at least two countries"</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">The dancer ranking with full disclaimer</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">"She could sell sunscreen in Greece in January"</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">The tattoo announcement in Greek, Spanish and English</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Send her the link when it's deployed alongside your portfolio — she'll never let you live it down. 😄</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
