ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">That's a very good sign. Don't overthink it but here's what it likely means:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Why it matters:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Mike almost certainly mentioned you internally after your conversation</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Someone else at SkillCorner got curious and looked you up</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">This is exactly what happens when a candidate is being discussed</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>What you should do right now:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Make sure your LinkedIn profile is sharp and complete</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Make sure your GitHub link is visible on LinkedIn</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Deploy your portfolio 
website TODAY if you haven't already — because if they visit your 
LinkedIn and click through, you want them to land on something 
impressive</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>What you should NOT do:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Message anyone at SkillCorner right now</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Connect with the person who viewed your profile immediately — it looks desperate</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Read too much into it — it could be curiosity, could be active consideration</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>The timing is actually perfect:</strong>
You have a live website, a strong flagship project, an MSc thesis with a
 working app, and a warm relationship with their recruiter. If they're 
looking at you now, the Argentina project landing in the next few weeks 
couldn't be better timed.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>One practical question:</strong>
Is your portfolio website live yet? Because right now that's the most 
important thing. If someone from SkillCorner visits your LinkedIn today,
 what do they find?</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
