          ease-[cubic-bezier(0.165,0.85,0.45,1)] h-8 w-8 rounded-md group/btn _fill_10ocf_9 _ghost_10ocf_96" type="button" data-testid="action-bar-copy" aria-label="Copy"><div class="relative text-text-500 group-hover/btn:text-text-100"><div class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="flex-shrink: 0;" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12.5 3A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 14 4.5V6h1.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 17 7.5v8a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 6 15.5V14H4.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 12.5v-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 3zm1.5 9.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H7v1.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5H14zM4.5 4a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5z"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute top-0 left-0 transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="flex-shrink: 0;" class="absolute top-0 left-0 transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15.188 5.11a.5.5 0 0 1 .752.626l-.056.084-7.5 9a.5.5 0 0 1-.738.033l-3.5-3.5-.064-.078a.501.501 0 0 1 .693-.693l.078.064 3.113 3.113 7.15-8.58z"></path></svg></div></div></button></div><div class="flex items-center"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-test-render-count="2"><div class="group" style="height: auto; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="contents"><div data-is-streaming="false" class="group relative relative pb-3" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">No problem. Here are the detailed steps specifically for adding a website link on LinkedIn:</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>On desktop (easiest way):</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong>linkedin.com</strong> and sign in</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click your profile photo in the top right → click <strong>View profile</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">You'll land on your profile page — look for a section near the top that shows your name, headline and location</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click the <strong>pencil icon</strong> in the top right of that section — this opens your intro editor</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Scroll down inside that editor until you see <strong>Contact info</strong> or <strong>Website</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>Add website</strong> or the <strong>+</strong> next to websites</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">In the <strong>URL</strong> field paste: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">https://yiannis-kastritis.github.io</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">In the <strong>Type</strong> dropdown select <strong>Portfolio</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>Apply</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Scroll to the bottom of the editor and click <strong>Save</strong></li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>If you can't find it that way, try this alternative:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">On your profile page scroll down until you see the <strong>Contact info</strong> section — it usually shows your email, LinkedIn URL etc.</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click the <strong>pencil icon</strong> next to Contact info</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">You'll see a <strong>Website</strong> field</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Add your URL there and save</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>On mobile:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Open the LinkedIn app</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Tap your profile photo → <strong>View profile</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Tap the <strong>pencil icon</strong> on your intro section</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Scroll down to <strong>Website</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Tap <strong>Add website</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Paste the URL and select <strong>Portfolio</strong> as the type</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Tap <strong>Save</strong> at the top right</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Which device are you doing this on — desktop or mobile? I can be even more specific if needed.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
