<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to github.com and open the repo</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Look at the <strong>right side</strong> of the page — you'll see an <strong>About</strong> section with a gear icon ⚙️ next to it</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click that <strong>gear icon</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">You'll see a <strong>Website</strong> field — paste your Streamlit URL there:</li>
</ol>
