<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Try this right now:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Open a new browser tab</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Type or paste <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">https://yiannis-kastritis.github.io</code> directly into the address bar</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Press Enter</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">It should load your portfolio site.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>If it's still not working:</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">The most likely issue is that you uploaded an older version of the <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">index.html</code> file — possibly before all our latest changes.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Check by looking at the file in your repo:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click on <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">index.html</code> in your repo</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click the <strong>Raw</strong> button</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Check if the content looks like your portfolio or if it's an older version</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Also — when you click the repo name <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">yiannis-kastritis.github.io</code> at the top, it opens the repo itself, not the website. The website is always at the separate URL <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">https://yiannis-kastritis.github.io</code>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Try opening that URL now and tell me what you see.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
