<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">These are simple and accurate — remember to type each one and press <strong>Enter</strong> or <strong>Space</strong> to confirm it as a separate pill before typing the next one.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Don't
 overthink the topics for this repo — it's your personal portfolio site,
 not a technical project. The topics matter much more on your <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">football-role-clustering</code> repo where people might actually search for that content.</p>
